
---

```http
### Point d'entrée API
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api
Accept: application/json

###

### Lister tous les calculs effectués
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/distances
Accept: application/json

###

### Calculer une distance valide (A=2,5 et B=1,6 → résultat attendu ≈ 1.414)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/distances
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_point": "2,5",
  "end_point": "1,6"
}

###

### Calculer une distance valide (triangle 3-4-5 → résultat attendu = 5.0)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/distances
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_point": "0,0",
  "end_point": "3,4"
}

###

### Erreur : coordonnées non numériques
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/distances
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_point": "abc,xyz",
  "end_point": "1,2"
}

###

### Erreur : champ manquant (end_point absent)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/distances
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_point": "0,0"
}

###

### Erreur : corps JSON vide
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/distances
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Erreur : requête sans corps
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/distances
